sentence: what states border the most populous state ?
sentence-with-vars: what states border the most populous state ?
sql: select border_info.border from border_info where border_info.state_name = ( select state.state_name from state where state.population = ( select max ( state.population ) from state ) ) ;
sql-with-vars: select border_info.border from border_info where border_info.state_name = ( select state.state_name from state where state.population = ( select max ( state.population ) from state ) ) ;
